ia-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104znw1665702832662.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/znw1665702832662.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/znw1665702832662.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"znw1665702832662\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Define Columns of List View\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define columns for the Tree widget's list view, and the way they are formatted in Details style.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znw1665702832662__p_d9431e1_d9432e1_d9433e1\">This dialog box enables you to define each column and its characteristics individually.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"znw1665702832662__note_w105ab1b5b3_w106ab1b5_w107ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If you want to dynamically change\n      these settings in ProcScript, you need to do so using the tree widget's Labels and Formats\n      properties. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lsq1707829945129.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsq1707829945129.html\" title=\"A label allows you to name a line of ProcScript. This line can then be branched to with a goto statement.\">ProcScript Labels</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sce1665702636971.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sce1665702636971.html\" title=\"Uniface list of properties that define the appearance of columns in the Details style of the list view of the tree widget.\">Formats</a>. </div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znw1665702832662__section_g2k_yvk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1110932e77\">Limits</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"znw1665702832662__ul_kfw_yvk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4286e1_d4287e1_d4288e1\">maximum number of columns = 127 </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4289e1_d4290e1_d4291e1\">maximum number of characters per column = 9999 </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4292e1_d4293e1_d4294e1\">maximum number of characters in column labels (LABELS\n          element of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span>) =1023\n        </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znw1665702832662__section_hjm_zvk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1110932e101\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"znw1665702832662__ul_ggf_1wk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4295e1_d4296e1_d4297e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tra1665702832875.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tra1665702832875.html\" title=\"Labels for columns that appear in the Details List View of the widget.\">Label</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4298e1_d4299e1_d4300e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dfb1665702636898.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfb1665702636898.html\" title=\"Sort order used for data displayed the selected column at run time.\">Sorting</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4301e1_d4302e1_d4303e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fsm1665702637040.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fsm1665702637040.html\" title=\"Character to be used for the decimal place indicator for numeric fields in the tree column.\">Decimal Indicator</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4304e1_d4305e1_d4306e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hvo1665702637111.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hvo1665702637111.html\" title=\"Specify how the label text is aligned in the selected column at run time.\">Alignment</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"znw1665702832662__li_d4307e1_d4308e1_d4309e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aie1665702637180.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aie1665702637180.html\" title=\"Width, in character cells, of the selected column.\">Column Width</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"znw1665702832662__section_lqp_jwk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1110932e155\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"znw1665702832662__p_d9473e1_d9474e1_d9475e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"moy1665702638031.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/moy1665702638031.html\" title=\"A tree widget is useful for displaying and maintaining hierarchical information.\">Defining Tree Widgets</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702634237.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>utree (Tree)</a><p>The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424469\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424469\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Columns of List View Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Columns of List View Define columns for the Tree widget's list view, and the way they are formatted in Details style. This dialog box enables you to define each column and its characteristics individually. Note: If you want to dynamically change these settings in ProcScript, you need to do so using the tree widget's Labels and Formats properties. For more information, see ProcScript Labels and Formats . Limits maximum number of columns = 127 maximum number of characters per column = 9999 maximum number of characters in column labels (LABELS element of $fieldproperties or $properties ) =1023 Fields Label Sorting Decimal Indicator Alignment Column Width How to Defining Tree Widgets Related Links utree (Tree) The utree widget enables users to view and navigate structured data as a hierarchy. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tree, which is mapped to utree. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}